properties.attributea: Accurate against Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS), FIPS Publication 6-4, and FIPS-55 at the 100% level for the codes and base names. The remaining attribute information has been examined but has not been fully tested for accuracy.

properties.title: NCA National Cemetery Boundaries 2014
properties.sourceorig: US Geological Survey - National Geospatial Technical Operations Center
properties.attributea: Names of cemeteries were provided by the National Cemetery Administration (NCA). Names were reviewed against NCA cemetery websites. Parcel boundaries and digitized boundaries were reviewed against orthorectified imagery. Area value was generated by USGS
properties.completene: This dataset contains boundary information for 133 National cemeteries. This is not a complete set of all lands administered or managed by the Department of Veterans Affairs or the National Cemetery Administration.
properties.horizposit: Accuracy varies by quality of source data. Overall dataset accuracy is comparable to USDA NAIP orthorectified imagery or better. The absolute accuracy has not been tested.
properties.sourcecont: The Office of Policy and Planning, National Center for Veterans Analysis and Statistics (NCVAS) and the National Cemetery Administration provided content direction and assistance with base data provision.
properties.metadatast: FGDC Content Standard for Digital Geospatial Metadata
